summary: Adds a spooky FX to invisible entities, making them partially visible.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds an effect to invisible entities, subsequently making them at least partially visible. This is a much more minimalistic approach compared to [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72165]Soultorn Entities[/url]ï»¿, but it looks very nice and fitting in-game.

Check the video and pictures to get a better idea of how it looks in-game.
author: CaucyBiops
